      ZERO       | ONE        | X          | Z      
ZERO  0 & 0 == 0 | 0 & 1 == 0 | 0 & x == 0 | 0 & z == 0 |
ONE   1 & 0 == 0 | 1 & 1 == 1 | 1 & x == x | 1 & z == x |
X     x & 0 == 0 | x & 1 == x | x & x == x | x & z == x |
Z     z & 0 == 0 | z & 1 == x | z & x == x | z & z == x |
